desc: Tonight: Showers, with thunderstorms also possible after 4am.  Low around 41. Northeast wind 5 to 10 mph.  Chance of precipitation is 100%. New rainfall amounts between a quarter and half of an inch possible.

Wednesday Night: Partly cloudy, with a low around 31. North northwest wind 10 to 15 mph.
Thursday: Sunny, with a high near 45. North wind 10 to 15 mph, with gusts as high as 20 mph.
Thursday Night: Mostly clear, with a low around 28. North northeast wind 5 to 10 mph.
Friday: Sunny, with a high near 52. East northeast wind 5 to 10 mph becoming southeast in the afternoon.
Friday Night: Partly cloudy, with a low around 39. South southeast wind around 10 mph.
Saturday: A 20 percent chance of showers after 7am.  Mostly cloudy, with a high near 60. South wind 10 to 15 mph, with gusts as high as 20 mph.
Saturday Night: A 20 percent chance of showers before 7pm.  Mostly cloudy, with a low around 48. South wind 5 to 10 mph.
